<div style="
    max-width: 640px;
    padding: 24px;
    border: 1px solid #D3D3D3;
    margin: 20px auto;
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #333;
    background-color: #ffffff;
">
    <div style="
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    ">
        <img src="cid:ethicappLogo" style="max-width: 200px;" alt="EthicApp Logo" />
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 16px;">Hello <strong><%= firstName %>,</strong></p>

    <p style="font-size: 16px;">
        Thank you for signing up with EthicApp. Just one more step to activate your account!
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 16px;">
        Please confirm your email address by clicking the button below. This verification helps us keep your account secure and provide you with a better experience on EthicApp.
    </p>

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
        <a href="<%= verificationUrl %>" style="
            background-color: #2649EC;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            font-size: 16px;
        ">
            Confirm My Email Address
        </a>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 16px;">
        If you did not request this registration, you can safely ignore this message.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>Best regards,</strong></p>
    <p style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>The EthicApp Team</strong></p>

    <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #777;">
        Welcome to EthicApp, where we build a deeper ethical learning experience together.
    </p>
</div>
